<p><strong>SCP-CN-1084：</strong>湖边的小屋燃烧殆尽<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/douglasliu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3728730); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3728730&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603968191" alt="DouglasLiu" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3728730)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/douglasliu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3728730); return false;">DouglasLiu</a></span>，作者页在<strong><a href="/douglasliu-author-page">此</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>配图修改自以下图片：</strong><br />
<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Lakeside_cabin_(Unsplash).jpg" target="_blank">Lakeside cabin</a>, Paul Gilmore, CC0</p>
