<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1084/scp-cn-1084-1.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="scp-cn-1084-1.jpg" class="image" />
